                         <p class="intro"><strong>EFFECTIVE AS OF DECEMBER 14, 2016</strong></p>
<div class="marB25">
<p>Rapid7 LLC and its affiliates (collectively, "we", "our", "us" or "Rapid7") are committed to your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how Rapid7 collects and uses the personal information you provide on our Web sites:&nbsp;<a href="http://mailer.samanage.com/wf/click?upn=kdoKU417pfxZETdSG0BEQInOKTj0CHn7S4HuqkA078E-3D_gQwze6ncMliH7HpG04sKDzlS63jRgzoGqOVfl2H5j-2Fbi9b3LaaFSL-2FgITt3TSkGNvAu4VwEavzMs7uP1zlpJMIC-2BFPnz7dlpN6aYuNBR-2FSslGQ8X1kh-2FdLx2N-2F-2BBthJ5vOiZjTMr5Bnc7SdUxM0qpq-2BMMe0EQI-2B5O5jXc5VzbKO-2F5uM0wP8GGZ1Iuou7F01m2f-2FGB3Fp-2BBtSjsUd68sKZzkRmwqq448EJTgQnWN7ZpYQgY2jz3RjZfuZZwvxi8hOKVqtwcUSM90SAQQ-2FNQvStQ8iwszNZYMqDdK3ZrzGg-2BAbjJiAkD2pMf6X9nyYXJLjgvAiuMMO2MIpwENRpllZaOjdy4XGAzAfr1DZB-2Bm-2FygGfZc-2F-2BQkRBbDnPQ-2B2ibJ3ybfQhnsiz5cw4eKV-2B24rXCc5zBdIF74qKZz3ZhveScf35Mmfe9AAIpzNTXhFP-2FgFjsbhM62KspW4EbdtSk1qqj1Dj9kLl447U6kXwoOdHQQsaq7FZ9gMMxBym2SmtUdwm" target="_blank"> www.rapid7.com </a>&nbsp;and&nbsp; <a href="http://mailer.samanage.com/wf/click?upn=kdoKU417pfxZETdSG0BEQAELsNjYBB4TgtqOBzjUt08-3D_gQwze6ncMliH7HpG04sKDzlS63jRgzoGqOVfl2H5j-2Fbi9b3LaaFSL-2FgITt3TSkGNvAu4VwEavzMs7uP1zlpJMIC-2BFPnz7dlpN6aYuNBR-2FSslGQ8X1kh-2FdLx2N-2F-2BBthJ5vOiZjTMr5Bnc7SdUxM0qpq-2BMMe0EQI-2B5O5jXc5VzbKO-2F5uM0wP8GGZ1Iuou7F01m2f-2FGB3Fp-2BBtSjsUd68sKZzkRmwqq448EJTgQnWN7ZpYQgY2jz3RjZfuZZwvxi8hOKVqtwcUSM90SAQQ-2FNQvStQ8iwszNZYMqDdK3ZrzGg-2BBX1fkcSXNmPNDmIyR6PzosGu0phn32khzUj6rPdcA-2BZRhCsI3E0X9KVKeGgZpqPXgmqA43FPvY5H5mvA22qLUPUaCYGDFZFKjF6c0p2sy71mlbUWJKawgWALLVbvm-2BYKUZhiX46Vz5Tw-2FHaLNUtU5ZoFTQNuS1oUwRPUjdcKDnXUKJgS85grd1aGipeVDheuEUlZAtfI7vRNcy9-2Bt2VcYw" target="_blank">www.metasploit.com</a>&nbsp;(each a "Site" and collectively, the "Sites") as well as the human resources data of our employees. It also describes the choices available to you regarding our use of your personal information and how you can access and update this information. We encourage you to read this Privacy Policy carefully when using the Site, or when providing information to us through the Site. You understand that by using the Site you are accepting our practices as described in this privacy statement.&nbsp;</p>
